data.description: Click the Tour 1 icon above for the NARRATED VIDEO VIRTUAL TOUR (not just the same still photos)!  The screened, tiled front entry is just the first of many attractions that this home offers.  Upon entering the living room, you notice right away that it is open to the dining area and kitchen, creating a true ‘great room’ that is perfect for family gatherings and entertaining friends.  That kitchen features upgraded wood cabinets and level 3 granite – both of which offer beauty and years and years of service.  Add in the breakfast bar, pantry closet and the brand-new range, and you have a kitchen that will delight any homemaker/amateur chef.  The family room is entered from the great room and has a pass through from the kitchen and French doors to the lanai.  The master’s 8’ X 7’ walk-in closet is large enough to satisfy any family as is its bathroom’s 7’ dual sink vanity.  Bedroom #2’s 12 long walk-in is a good match to the master’s.  So is the guest bathroom’s 7’ 6” dual sink vanity.  No vanity sink sharing is needed in this fine home!  Bedroom #3 is graced with lots of windows, so it is perfect for a hobby room or office – plentiful natural light.  A coat closet, 2 linen closets, a garage storage closet, and pull-down attic stairs offer more storage than usually found in a home this size.  Tile plank flooring was added to the master bedroom and the 2nd bedroom for looks and ease of cleaning.  New roof, new exterior paint, and 4 new impact-resistant windows defer some big costs for the new owners.  The white vinyl fence, nice, screened lanai, and a large, covered patio add gracious outdoor living to a very comfortable indoors.  This property comes with a ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY. Much, much more info is attached – ask your agent for copies, especially the FEATURES LIST.
